H0.text: I Drove All Night in 1993 was the last solo UK chart entry for which singer. Elvis Presley

H1.text: I Drove All Night in 1993 was the last solo UK chart entry for which singer. Roy Orbison

H2.text: I Drove All Night in 1993 was the last solo UK chart entry for which singer. Tom Jones

H3.text: I Drove All Night in 1993 was the last solo UK chart entry for which singer. Orbison

A4.text: Roy Orbison's version of 'I Drove All Night' reached number 7 on the UK Singles Chart in 1992.

A5.text: Cyndi Lauper's version of 'I Drove All Night' was a top-10 hit in the UK in 1989.
